# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# airlock-config (describe · discover)  —  .env.example
#
# Template. Copy to `.env` (gitignored) if you ever need it:  cp .env.example .env
#
# airlock-config's core toolchain needs NO credentials: validate, preflight,
# sandbox, build, agent-card, register-entry, and search all run offline and
# emit static files or PR-ready JSON. You self-list in the registry by opening
# a PR (no push token), and search reads a public GitHub-hosted JSON index (no
# token). So this template is intentionally near-empty — no Cloudflare, no
# wallet, no API keys.
#
# The entry below is for a PLANNED feature only; it is not wired yet. Uncomment
# when the corresponding feature ships.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Agent Card signing (v0.6 · planned, not yet implemented) ─────────────────
# ECDSA P-256 private key (JWK or PEM) used by the future `sign-card` command.
# AIRLOCK_CONFIG_SIGNING_KEY=
